data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!! Situated in the highly desired Community of Willow Square, Residents can enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and dining, with easy access to all major roads and highways.This exquisite townhome offers three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and a one-car garage. This property exemplifies immaculate pride of ownership and the stainless steel appliances complement the interior, which features a convenient open floor plan, tile flooring throughout common areas, and crown molding throughout.   Additionally, it offers a serene enclosed lanai overlooking the nearby nature preserve.    This townhome provides a perfect balance of comfort and style. Residents can enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and dining, with easy access to all major roads and highways. Experience the best of both worlds - the tranquility of a peaceful neighborhood, with all of the Tampa Bay Area's excitement just moments away.
